  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a world where living disasters have eradicated people’s homes, the protagonist sets out on a journey with Hounimal, the village guardian, to restore homes to the world. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Collect and Place Furniture</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185010/extras/31f3cad0d302be918035696f009d756d.poster.avif?t=1767672800\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185010/extras/31f3cad0d302be918035696f009d756d.webm?t=1767672800\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185010/extras/31f3cad0d302be918035696f009d756d.mp4?t=1767672800\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Obtain various pieces of furniture during your journey and place them in Hounimal. The actions you can choose in battle will change depending on the furniture. (Of course, you can also enjoy them as interior decorations!) </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Simultaneous Turn-Based Command Battles</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185010/extras/4fe6e252b65cfb26d5fff60e29439b1f.poster.avif?t=1767672800\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185010/extras/4fe6e252b65cfb26d5fff60e29439b1f.webm?t=1767672800\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185010/extras/4fe6e252b65cfb26d5fff60e29439b1f.mp4?t=1767672800\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A unique command battle system where turns progress simultaneously with the enemy.</strong> Strategically link commands using randomly obtained resources and control the action order to lead your Hounimals to victory. If you're lost, you can pause the action and take your time to plan!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Rebuild Your Base</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185010/extras/bc044c641579100d8600a19dde45ee07.poster.avif?t=1767672800\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185010/extras/bc044c641579100d8600a19dde45ee07.webm?t=1767672800\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185010/extras/bc044c641579100d8600a19dde45ee07.mp4?t=1767672800\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock features that give you an edge in your journey using magic nails obtained on your adventures. Draw out even more of your Hounimals' power.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a world where living disasters have eradicated people’s homes, the protagonist sets out on a journey with Hounimal, the village guardian, to restore homes to the world. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Collect and Place Furniture</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185010/extras/31f3cad0d302be918035696f009d756d.poster.avif?t=1767672800\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185010/extras/31f3cad0d302be918035696f009d756d.webm?t=1767672800\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185010/extras/31f3cad0d302be918035696f009d756d.mp4?t=1767672800\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Obtain various pieces of furniture during your journey and place them in Hounimal. The actions you can choose in battle will change depending on the furniture. (Of course, you can also enjoy them as interior decorations!) </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Simultaneous Turn-Based Command Battles</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185010/extras/4fe6e252b65cfb26d5fff60e29439b1f.poster.avif?t=1767672800\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185010/extras/4fe6e252b65cfb26d5fff60e29439b1f.webm?t=1767672800\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185010/extras/4fe6e252b65cfb26d5fff60e29439b1f.mp4?t=1767672800\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A unique command battle system where turns progress simultaneously with the enemy.</strong> Strategically link commands using randomly obtained resources and control the action order to lead your Hounimals to victory. If you're lost, you can pause the action and take your time to plan!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Rebuild Your Base</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185010/extras/bc044c641579100d8600a19dde45ee07.poster.avif?t=1767672800\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185010/extras/bc044c641579100d8600a19dde45ee07.webm?t=1767672800\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3185010/extras/bc044c641579100d8600a19dde45ee07.mp4?t=1767672800\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock features that give you an edge in your journey using magic nails obtained on your adventures. Draw out even more of your Hounimals' power.</p>",
